title: Ep - 123 - JORDAN KIMBALL FROM BACHELORETTE AND BACHELOR OF PARADISE
description:
Jordan Kimball from Becca’s season of The Bachelorette and Bachelor in Paradise talks about how he was cast for the show, what really happened in Paradise with Tia and Colton and the other couples, how he helped The Goose (Chris Randone) with his confidence, and where you can buy his hibiscus suit. 


Acting coach Dana Bowling helps Kate review MTV’s new show Pretty Little Mamas, which follows a group of five young moms raising kids in San Diego.


And Kate review this week’s episode of Alaskan Bush People with Arizona based attorney Casey Yontz. Neither of them had ever seen the show prior.


Reality Life with Kate Casey
